        "text": "# CHICKEN OR THE EGG?\nSo, how do chickens and eggs inter-relate? Well I believe that if there are more chickens\nthere will be more eggs. In the language of systems thinking we would capture this as\nfollows:\n"
      },
      "date": 1611663777674
    },
