      "type": "add",
      "id": "fd81b6653b445c9f",
      "item": {
        "type": "markdown",
        "id": "fd81b6653b445c9f",
        "text": "This is shorthand for “the number of chickens affects (arrow) the number of eggs in the\nsame (S) direction all other things being held equal”.\nSimilarly, if there are more eggs, there will be more chickens.\n"
      },
      "after": "41a790e6f9069ca4",
      "date": 1611663785151
